    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[故事]</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/4da850103019a825b588dc9fdf221766.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/4da850103019a825b588dc9fdf221766.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/4da850103019a825b588dc9fdf221766.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由“秩序女神”和“混沌女神”统治的“Andalun”和“Confunia”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一天，混乱女神消失了，怪物女王出现在Confunia。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了遏制魔物女王，秩序骑士团长“Travon”奉秩序女神之命远征康芙尼亚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这次远征，“Travon”亲自获得了孔夫尼亚所有怪物女王的效忠誓言，成为孔夫尼亚的霸主，并与安达隆缔结了和平条约。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而“Travon”则陷入了沉睡，以控制他从怪物女王那里获得的力量…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许久之后，当他醒来时，承诺的平安并不存在。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>玩法]</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/fb252dfb10adb6282ad240d2745ebafe.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/fb252dfb10adb6282ad240d2745ebafe.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/fb252dfb10adb6282ad240d2745ebafe.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团结四散的怪物女王，重夺你的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级，强化每位女王的属性和技能，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并让破坏和平协议的敌人付出代价。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>游戏特色]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有吸引力的角色 （13个可玩角色）</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/f99d921bd93afa046083c71bc1865811.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/f99d921bd93afa046083c71bc1865811.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/f99d921bd93afa046083c71bc1865811.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的故事</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/cdbbd9fb1b2f65882d7b7a03475a83c6.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/cdbbd9fb1b2f65882d7b7a03475a83c6.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/cdbbd9fb1b2f65882d7b7a03475a83c6.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通过各种角色组合进行战斗</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/1169492cffdef11269d6e7bd9476c44a.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/1169492cffdef11269d6e7bd9476c44a.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/1169492cffdef11269d6e7bd9476c44a.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通过技能和属性分配，打造属于你自己的角色</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/bd2a0c05b7b8bc55f6759c1d82a2c150.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/bd2a0c05b7b8bc55f6759c1d82a2c150.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/bd2a0c05b7b8bc55f6759c1d82a2c150.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每个角色都有番外篇和额外书籍</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/8dcd14fc4a06c03daa315102c629fda6.poster.avif?t=1765328572\" width=1170 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/8dcd14fc4a06c03daa315102c629fda6.webm?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841360/extras/8dcd14fc4a06c03daa315102c629fda6.mp4?t=1765328572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
